<br>
On my server (AB) it's getting difficult to get this camp though. Quite a few different classes seem to be heading this way. But, I still think it's the perfect 24-29 mage spot. Although I must admit it's fun watching mid-30 melee types having difficulty with mobs I could solo at 20  :P<br>
